♪ Traces of existence
can never be erased ♪

279
00:13:32,710 --> 00:13:35,990
♪ How to find the self I can't reclaim ♪

280
00:13:38,300 --> 00:13:45,370
♪ Fly away, hear she says ♪

281
00:13:45,450 --> 00:13:49,406
♪ She'll fly out from
thorns of woven lies ♪

282
00:13:49,430 --> 00:13:53,006
♪ Pierce the fog,
shatter this dream tonight ♪

283
00:13:53,030 --> 00:13:55,966
♪ Burn like fire ♪

284
00:13:55,990 --> 00:13:59,400
♪ Just burn like fire ♪

285
00:13:59,620 --> 00:14:03,500
♪ The maze in the abyss starts to clear ♪

286
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:06,226
♪ Yet night keep on whispering ♪

287
00:14:06,250 --> 00:14:09,390
♪ Surrender to fate,
no clear direction ahead ♪

288
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:13,180
♪ She will rise as the dawn
that breaks the darkness ♪

289
00:14:13,250 --> 00:14:19,710
♪ Never slowing down,
for tomorrow cannot be stopped ♪

290
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:23,676
♪ Surrender to love and find the way ♪

291
00:14:23,700 --> 00:14:27,230
♪ Even if fate tries to forget her ♪

292
00:14:27,450 --> 00:14:33,980
♪ Never despair,
for the heart burns with endless light ♪

293
00:14:34,390 --> 00:14:36,240
♪ Waiting for dawn ♪

